bug.short_desc: [regression] Out of memory when preview the attached report with crosstab in Web Viewer [1102]

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 85970 report design
Description: Out of memory when preview the attached report with crosstab in Web Viewer.

Steps to reproduce: 1. Preview the attached report in Web Viewer.

Actual result: Out of memory and it works fine in build (2.3.0.v20071221-1008).

The same cause with bug 214074.
